reviewText: Elmo's World DVD is great, I believe it has Ears too.  Our autistic son loves Elmo's World and has learned a great deal from the individual segments.

Very well done with plenty of Elmo for Elmo fans. No advertisements on front end. My 18-month old can put it into the player and watch it over and over. It is amazing what kids can learn from these classic Sesame Street programs.
